OL,3,C#1.2m damages award for men abused by
OL,4,Cpriest
OL,6,FFive former pupils who claimed a
OL,7,Fpaedophile priest groomed and abused
OL,8,Fthem at a Co Down school are to
OL,9,Freceive more than #1.2m in combined
OL,10,Fdamages, it has emerged.
OL,12,FThe compensation forms part of
OL,13,Fsettlements reached in the men's High
OL,14,FCourt actions over alleged historic
OL,15,Fsexual and physical assaults
OL,16,Fperpetrated by the late Father Malachy
OL,17,FFinegan.
