OL,6,FWritten apologies will also be issued
OL,7,Fto them from the head of the Catholic
OL,8,FChurch in Ireland as part of the
OL,9,Fresolutions, their solicitor disclosed.
OL,11,FThe plaintiffs, who cannot be
OL,12,Fidentified, sued the Diocese of
OL,13,FDromore and the Board of Governors at
OL,14,FSt Colman's College in Newry over
OL,15,Ffailures to protect him from the
OL,16,Fpriest.
OL,18,FThey all attended the school as young
OL,19,Fboys over a period spanning between
OL,20,F1972 and 1984.
