OL,6,FDuring that time Finegan, who taught
OL,7,Fand worked at the college, subjected
OL,8,Fthem to serious sexual, physical and
OL,9,Femotional abuse, according to their
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FLawyers for the five men described the
OL,13,Falleged molestation as "depraved and
OL,14,Fsadistic".
OL,16,FFinegan was accused of a wider
OL,17,Fcampaign of child sexual abuse but
OL,18,Fnever prosecuted or questioned by
OL,19,Fpolice about claims made against him.
