OL,6,FHe died in 2002, but years later it
OL,7,Femerged that the Diocese of Dromore
OL,8,Fhad settled a previous case taken by
OL,9,Fone of his alleged victims.
OL,11,FAt that stage the Board of Governors
OL,12,Fat St Colman's condemned the physical,
OL,13,Fsexual and emotional abuse inflicted
OL,14,Fby Finnegan who also served as its
OL,15,Fpresident.
OL,17,FSince then a series of lawsuits have
OL,18,Fbeen mounted over the alleged failures
OL,19,Fto prevent him from targeting pupils.
