OL,4,Cpriest
OL,6,FThe latest group of five claims had
OL,7,Fbeen scheduled for trial hearings at
OL,8,Fthe High Court in Belfast.
OL,10,FInstead, however, further settlements
OL,11,Fwere confirmed today without any
OL,12,Fadmission of liability by the
OL,13,Fdefendants.
OL,15,FOne of the group spoke about how
OL,16,FFinegan preyed on him as a vulnerable
OL,17,Fboy by grooming and abusing for his
OL,18,Fown pleasure.
