OL,3,C#1.2m damages award for men abused by
OL,4,Cpriest
OL,6,FQuestioning why nothing was done to
OL,7,Fstop the priest's activities, he also
OL,8,Fdescribed suffering severe anxiety,
OL,9,Fnightmares and PTSD in the intervening
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FOutside court solicitor Claire
OL,13,FMcKeegan of Phoenix Law, who
OL,14,Frepresents all five plaintiffs,
OL,15,Frevealed that their combined total
OL,16,Fcompensation "exceeded #1.2m".
OL,18,FShe confirmed they are now to receive
OL,19,Fletters of apology from Archbishop
OL,20,FEamon Martin, Primate of Ireland, on
OL,21,Fbehalf of the Diocese of Dromore.
